<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3149> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3149" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "A candidate for the consulship between 132, his brother's consulship, and the death of Scipio in 129 (Fannius fr. 6 Peter; Cic. Lael. 73; Plin. NH 7.122). Accordingly 133 is the latest date possible for his praetorship under the Lex Villia." .
